summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 73W, Page 173 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located in Coffman Garden Tracts from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to General Commercial (CG) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Gordon Brown; C.F. 270372).
